## DATA FLOW

```
STEP file
  │
  ▼ [mesh_step.py: PythonOCC + Gmsh API]
  ├── mesh.msh           (Gmsh v2 format)
  └── face_map.json      (CAD face ID → mesh element/node IDs)
  │
  ▼ [C# MeshingService → deserialize]
  MeshData (nodes, elements, face groups)
  │
  ▼ [User: face selection, BC/load assignment in WPF UI]
  FEAModel (MeshData + BCs + Loads + Material)
  │
  ▼ [write_inp.py]
  model.inp
  │
  ▼ [SolverService: ccx.exe model]
  model.frd + model.dat
  │
  ▼ [parse_frd.py]
  results.json (node displacements, von Mises stress per node)
  │
  ▼ [C# ResultService → deserialize → HelixToolkit colormap]
  3D stress/displacement visualization
```

