## ERROR HANDLING

| Scenario | Detection | Response |
|----------|-----------|----------|
| ccx.exe not found | ConfigService startup check | Alert user, open config dialog |
| Python not found | subprocess OSError | Alert user with install instructions |
| Gmsh mesh failure | Non-zero exit code + stderr | Display stderr in log panel |
| ccx divergence | Parse .dat for "NO CONVERGENCE" | Show warning, display partial results |
| Under-constrained model | ccx singular matrix error in stdout | Warn: "model may be under-constrained" |
| STEP import failure | OCC exception in mesh_step.py | Propagate error message to UI |
| Missing face_map | FileNotFoundError after meshing | Re-run meshing |

